PM Indiya zai halarci haikali a wurin da ake takaddama akai
NEW DELHI (AP) - Firaministan Indiya Narendra Modi zai halarci bikin bazara na watan gobe na haikalin Hindu a kan wani wuri da ake takaddama a arewacin Indiya inda wani masallaci na ƙarni na 16 ya rushe da masu kishin addinin Hindu a shekarar 1992, bisa ga amincewar da ke kula da ginin haikali.
An kafa bikin ne don Aug. 5, wani ranar da aka shirya ya ce an yi wa Hindus astrologically m amma kuma cewa ya nuna shekara tun da majalisar dokokin Indiya ta sake kiran semi-autonomous matsayin ta kawai Muslim-majority jihar, Jammu da Kashmir.
A alamance ba zai yiwu ba ga magoya baya da kuma abokan adawar Modi na Hindu nationalist Bharatiya Janata Party, ko BJP, wanda manifesto da shekaru da yawa da suka hada da alkawuran da za su huta Kashmir ta mulkin kai da kuma gina haikali ga Hindu god Ram inda masallacin Mughal-era da zarar ya tsaya, wani wuri a birnin Ayodhya a jihar Uttar Pradesh da masu ibada suka yi imani da zama Ram ta haihuwa.
Domin har yanzu cutar korona na ci gaba da yaduwa a fadin kasar Indiya, wadda ta ba da rahoton harka ta uku a duniya, za a watsa bikin a gidan talabijin na jihar kuma za a takaita yawan mahalarta da 'yan kallo, a cewar Vishwa Hindu Parishad, ko Kungiyar Hindu ta Duniya, kungiyar Hindu mai kishin kasa tare da BJP.
Haikalin zai yi hidima a matsayin "matukar da ba ta mutuwa ba, cibiyar jituwa ta zamantakewa, hadin kan kasa da hadewa da kuma farkawa na jin Hindutva," ko kuma hanyar Hindu ta rayuwa, kakakin kungiyar Vinod Bansal ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa Asabar.
An warware rikice-rikice na ƙarni a kan shafin a bara bayan nasarar da jam'iyyar BJP ta samu a zaben ƙasar.
A watan Nuwamba, Kotun Koli ta yanke hukuncin amincewa da amincewar haikalin, tana mai cewa za a ba da roƙon Musulmi biyar eka a wani madadin site.
Masu kishin addinin Hindu sun dade suna kokawa da cewa Mughal Musulmi masu mamaye gina masallaci a saman wani haikalin da ya gabata a birnin Ayodya na dā.
Wata tarzoma ta watan Disamba na shekarar 1992 da ta biyo bayan rushe masallacin ta haifar da tashin hankali inda aka kashe mutane kimanin 2,000, galibinsu Musulmi.
A halin da ake ciki, ana ci gaba da sauraron shari’ar a kotun daukaka kara ta musamman.
Wani mai gine-gine daga Ahmedabad, Gujarat, jihar Modi ta gida, ya samar da tsarin sandstone mai hasumiya 161 (minti 49) mai tsawo tare da domes biyar.
Yogi Adityanath, babban ministan Uttar Pradesh da kuma wani dan Hindu, ya buƙaci cewa Ayodhya ya riƙe bikin tsabtace da tsarkakewa na musamman da kuma ga dukan haikalin birnin zuwa fitilu masu haske na man fetur gabanin ziyarar Modi, kamfanin dillancin labarai na Press Trust na India ya ruwaito.
Adityanath ya ce bikin ya nuna cewa an kawo karshen "karar da shekara 500", in ji PTI.
