Ka yi gargaɗin lambun gimmicks da ke sa su yi kyau
Yana iya zama abin kunya ga masanin tsirrai ya yarda, amma ni ne total sucker ga lambu gimmick.
Ina so in yi tunani shi ne saboda ni ne bude ko kuma watakila kawai irrationally fatauci, musamman kamar yadda abubuwa da yawa a cikin shuka duniya ne sau da yawa musamman counterintuitive.
Amma ba ni da kunya in ce na auku domin da dama daga cikinsu a tsawon rayuwa a gonaki.
Duk da yake na yi imani da darajar kokarin abubuwa fitar da kanka, idan ba ka zato koyon hanya mai wuya, a nan ne wasu daga cikin mafi yawan lambu gimmicks na zo a fadin.
Da farko, kuma mai yiwuwa mafi munin laifi, grafted tumatir-potato shuke-shuke.
Haifa a matsayin juyin juya halin nasara, grafting tumatir shuke-shuke a kan tushen dankali ne, a gaskiya, wani tsohon makaranta botanical curiosity, dating back to a kalla 1920s.
Kamar yadda su biyu ne daga cikin iyali guda kuma suna da kama da ciki "plumbing," za ka iya lalle halitta irin wannan surgically inganta al'ajabi.
Amma a nan ne matsalar: samar da tsari mai mahimmanci kamar 'ya'yan itatuwa da tushe yana ɗaukar makamashi mai yawa na metabolic, kuma idan shuke-shuke suna ƙoƙarin yin amfani da ƙarfinsu na iyaka babu makawa ya zama raba.
Wannan yana nufin yadda ake amfani da waɗannan tsire-tsire masu ƙarfe suke da ban tsoro kuma babu abin da kake gani a cikin hotuna na tallace-tallace.
Sa'an nan kuma akwai gaskiyar cewa amfanin gonar sun balaga a lokuta daban-daban, don haka don girbi da spuds dole ne ka kashe shuke-shuke kafin tumatir ya ripened.
A kan batun tallace-tallace imagery, akwai da yawa dodgy mu'amala a nan, ma.
Na ga roses Photoshopped sama blue da 'ya'yan itatuwan da physiologically ba zai yiwu adadin 'ya'yan itace a kan rassan su a wasu manyan kasidu.
Na ma gani hotuna "borrowed" daga asusun Instagram da kuma shafukan yanar gizo masu sayayya a matsayin hotunan filaye na gwaji.
Abin baƙin ciki, aikin ƙananan ƙananan kamfanoni na cavalier yana nufin cewa dole ne ka duba hotunan talla, musamman a kan layi, tare da idon basira sosai.
Idan yana da kyau ya zama gaskiya, mai yiwuwa.
Da yake magana game da abin da, da launi blue ne in mun gwada rare a cikin botanical duniya, don haka idan ka ga wani dazzling sabon heather, orchid ko cactus, shining fita a cikin mafi m "disinfectant" inuwa na blue, shi ne kusan lalle an fesa ko dyed.
Wanne zai zama lafiya, muddin masu sayarwa suka bayyana wannan, amma da wuya su taba yi.
Blue moth orchids za su sake mayar da su asali fari, amma sprayed cacti da heathers, rufi a cikin wani haske-suppressing Layer na dye, ba zai yiwu ba su tsira tsawon.
A ƙarshe, dole ne in flag up bonsai kits ko, ko ma mafi muni, bonsai tsaba, cewa alkawarin miniature itatuwa zai yayyafa daga su fakitoci.
Bonsai ba nau'in tsiro ba ne.
Hanyar horarwa ce da ake amfani da ita don ba da haskaka da itatuwa na dā a kan duwatsu masu nisa.
An kusan ko da yaushe fara daga balagagge shrubs da aka hacked baya da sabon girma waya a wuri.
Na san zan ci gaba da faɗuwa don gimmicks, yana da ɓangare na fun na gwaji.
Amma a gefe-mataki wadannan kuma kana iya samun wanda a zahiri yana da damar yin rayuwa har zuwa alkawarinsa.
Kotu ta bude wuta yayin zanga-zanga a California
OAKLAND, Ca. -- Masu zanga-zanga a California sun bude wuta a gaban kotu, sun lalata ofishin 'yan sanda da kuma cin zarafin jami'ai bayan da zanga-zangar lumana ta tsananta a yammacin Asabar, inji 'yan sandan Oakland.
Masu zanga-zanga sun fasa tagogi, sun fesa fentin zane-zane, sun harbe wuta da kuma nuna Lasers a jami’an, sashen Oakland ya ce a Twitter .
Kafofin watsa labarai da dama sun yi kira ga zaman lafiya kuma sun nemi masu shiryawa da su " taimaka mana mu samar da wurare masu hadari da kuma wuraren da za su iya zama masu zanga-zanga."
An fara zanga-zangar ne a farkon ranar Asabar da yamma tare da kungiyoyi irin su "Wall of Moms," kama daga wata kungiyar da ta kafa a Portland, Oregon, yayin da masu zanga-zangar suka fuskanci jami'an Amurka da aka tura zuwa wannan birnin don tsare wani gidan gwamnatin tarayya.
Shugaba Donald Trump ya aike da jami'an gwamnatin tarayya don matsa lamba a kan zanga-zangar da ta auku cikin dare tun bayan mutuwar George Floyd a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu.
Zanga-zangar da aka yi a Oakland ta fara lumana, amma ta juya baya cikin dare.
Jami'an 'yan sanda sun ayyana wani taron "unlawful assembly" da misalin karfe 11:30 na dare kuma jami'ai sun nemi jama'a su tarwatsa.
Wutar ta tashi ne a unguwar Alameda County Superior Court kuma tana dauke ne da dan kankanin lokaci daga baya, kamfanin dillancin labarai ya ruwaito.
Jami'an 'yan sanda sun ce masu zanga-zanga a wani lokaci "sun yi taho mu gama da tagogi da kuma rera wakokin nuna wariyar launin fata a mazauna wurin."
Hotunan da sashen ya bayar sun nuna gilashin da fenti mai karya garkuwar jiki a wani ginin 'yan sanda.
Muhimmancin Tsaro a wajen Ofishin Jakadancin Amurka a Chengdu, China
An samu tsauraran tsaro a wajen ofishin jakadancin Amurka a birnin Chengdu na kasar Sin ranar Lahadi, yayin da ma'aikatan Amurka suka shirya barin wuraren.
An ga motoci uku masu motsi suna shiga cikin ginin fili, yayin da 'yan sanda masu zaman kansu suka yi layi a duka bangarorin titi, wanda aka yi layi da shinge na karfe.
Editan jaridar tabloid na kasar Sin ya ce an bai wa ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke birnin Chengdu sa'o'i 72 zuwa kusa, ko kuma har zuwa karfe 10 na safe (0200GMT) Litinin, 27 ga watan Yuli.
China ta tuhumi wasu ma'aikata a ofishin jakadancin Chengdu da cewa, "ayyuka ne da ba su dace da ganewa ba."
Ba tare da bayar da cikakken bayani ba, mai magana da yawun ma'aikatar harkokin wajen kasar Sin, Wang Wenbin ya ce irin wannan aiki ya tsoma baki a harkokin kasar Sin kuma ya cutar da sha'anin tsaronta.
An bayar da umurnin rufe ofishin jakadancin kasar Sin da ke birnin Chengdu a ranar Juma'ar da ta gabata a dalilin ramuwar gayya ga umurnin Amurka na rufe ofishin jakadancin kasar Sin da ke birnin Houston na jihar Texas.
Washington ta umarci China ta rufe ofishin Houston "don kare dukiyar masana'antu ta Amurka da bayanan sirri."
Yayin da rufe ofishin jakadancin kasar Sin da ke Houston ya faru a ranar Juma'a, an ga wasu maza da suka bayyana su a matsayin jami'an Amurka suna fasa-kwaurin zuwa wurin da aka bude ta bakin kofa.
Wang ya ce a ranar Asabar din da ta gabata, ya keta yarjejeniyoyin kasa da kasa da kuma Sin za su amsa, ba tare da kayyade yadda za su yi ba.
Kulle-kulle na titin ya kara rura wutar tashin hankalin da ke tsakanin kasashen biyu kan batutuwa daga ciniki da leken asirin masana'antu zuwa kare hakkin bil Adama.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce dubban masu gwagwarmayar yaki da Pakistan a Afghanistan
ISLAMABAD -- Wani rahoto na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ce sama da 'yan awaren Pakistan 6,000 ne ke boye a Afghanistan, mafi yawansu na cikin kungiyar Taliban da aka hambarar da ita da ke da alhakin kai hari kan sojojin Pakistan da kuma farar hula.
Rahoton da aka fitar a wannan makon ya ce kungiyar, wadda aka fi sani da Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP), ta na da alaka da kungiyar da ke da alaka da Afghanistan da kungiyar IS.
Wasu daga cikin mambobin kungiyar TTP ma sun shiga kungiyar IS, wacce ke da hedkwatarta a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afghanistan ba ta amsa tambayoyin da kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya aiko ba.
Rahoton ya ce kungiyar IS a Afghanistan, wadda aka fi sani da IS a lardin Khorasan, ta yi fama da matsalar tsaro a Afghanistan da kuma sojojin Amurka da na NATO, har ma a wani lokaci da Taliban ta Afghanistan.
An shirya rahoton ne ta hanyar tawagar masu nazari da kuma sa ido kan takunkumin Amurka, wadda ke lura da kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda a duniya.
Rahoton ya kiyasta membobin kungiyar IS a Afghanistan da 2,200, kuma yayin da shugabancinta ya ruguje, IS har yanzu tana kirga a tsakanin shugabanninta dan kasar Syria Abu Said Mohammad al-Khorasani.
Rahoton ya kuma ce tawagar masu sa ido ta samu bayanai da ke cewa manyan kwamandojin Islama biyu, Abu Qutaibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraqi, sun iso Afghanistan ne daga Gabas ta Tsakiya.
"Ko da yake a yankin baya baya, (harkar Musulunci) ya rage iya kai hare-hare masu tsauri a sassa daban-daban na kasar, ciki har da Kabul.
Yana kuma da nufin jawo hankalin mayakan Taliban da ke adawa da yarjejeniyar da Amurka," in ji rahoton, yana mai nuni da yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya da Amurka ta kulla da Taliban a watan Fabrairu.
An cimma wannan yarjejeniyar ne don ba da damar Amurka ta kawo karshen shekaru 19 da take da hannu a Afghanistan, kuma kiraye-kirayen kungiyar Taliban ta tabbatar da yankinta ba za ta yi amfani da kungiyoyin ta’addanci ba.
Haka kuma ana sa ran yarjejeniyar za ta tabbatar da hadin gwiwar kungiyar Taliban a yaki da IS.
Kashi na biyu kuma watakila mafi mahimmanci a cikin yarjejeniyar ya bukaci tattaunawa tsakanin Taliban da shugabannin siyasar Kabul.
A ranar Asabar din da ta gabata ne, ma’aikatar harkokin wajen Amurka ta fitar da wata sanarwa inda ta ce jakadanta na zaman lafiya Zalmay Khalilzad ya sake shuka yankin da ke neman tsalle ya fara wannan tattaunawar, wanda aka dage a kai a kai yayin da bangarorin biyu suka yi kaurin suna wajen shirin sakin fursuna.
Yarjejeniyar da Amurka ta cimma ta bukaci gwamnatin Afghanistan da ta saki fursunoni 5,000 na Taliban da kuma Taliban don 'yantar da gwamnati da sojoji 1,000 a matsayin abin da ake kira kyakkyawan zato a gaban tattaunawa.
Har ya zuwa yanzu gwamnati ta ki sakin fursunonin Taliban kusan 600 da ta kira masu aikata manyan laifuka kuma ta ba da kyauta.
Kungiyar Taliban ta ki amincewa.
"Jam'iyyun sun fi kusa da fara tattaunawar atra-Afghan, muhimmin mataki na gaba na kawo karshen yakin Afghanistan na shekaru 40", in ji sanarwar Ma'aikatar harkokin wajen Amurka.
"Ko da yake an samu gagarumin ci gaba a kan musayar fursuna, batun na bukatar ƙarin ƙoƙari don warwarewa sosai."
Kakakin kungiyar Taliban na siyasa a farkon makon nan ya ce a shirye yake ya gudanar da tattaunawa da shugabannin siyasar Kabul bayan hutun Musulunci na Eid al-Adha a karshen watan nan, inda ya samar da an kammala sakin fursuna.
Babban abin damuwa ga Pakistan shi ne kasancewar Afghanistan na 'yan gwagwarmaya, musamman wadanda ke da alaka da TTP ko Jamaat-ul-Ahrar ko Lashkar-e-Islam, da kuma wadanda ke da Baluchistan Liberation Army, wadda ta dauki alhakin kai hare-hare masu tsauri a wannan watan a kudancin lardin Sindh da kuma a kudu maso yammacin lardin Baluchistan.
An kashe sojojin Pakistan da dama a wannan watan a lardin Baluchistan da ke kudu maso yammacin kasar a fafatawa da mayakan sa kai.
TTP ta dauki alhakin daya daga cikin hare-hare mafi muni a Pakistan a 2014, lokacin da aka kai hari makarantar sojojin Pakistan kuma an kashe 140.
