A halin yanzu 'yan sanda suna gudanar da bincike a kan jerin kalaman da aka wallafa kan asusun yanar gizo na Grime.
Sakataren Gida ya fada a ranar Lahadi cewa: "Abubuwa masu karya garkuwar jiki daga Wiley suna da ban tsoro."
"Ya kamata ba su iya kasancewa a Twitter da Instagram tsawon lokaci ba kuma na nemi cikakken bayani."
"Kamfanin kafofin watsa labarun dole ne su yi saurin kawar da irin wannan kiyayya daga cikin dandamali."
An zargi Twitter da "mutumin karya" yayin da har yanzu Wiley tweets suna bayyane sa'o'i 12 bayan an fara wallafa su.
Tun da farko an cire tweets da dama kuma an fitar da 41-year-old a cikin kwana bakwai da shafin.
Twitter a baya ya ce an kulle asusun Wiley na ɗan lokaci "don karya manufofinmu na ƙiyayya," yayin da Facebook ya ce "babu wani wuri don kalaman kiyayya a kan Instagram."
