Coronavirus: An gaya wa matafiya daga Spain su kebe
Matafiya da suka isa Birtaniya daga Spain yanzu dole ne a kebe su na kwanaki 14, a karkashin sabbin dokokin tafiya ta coronavirus.
An sanar da su a ranar Asabar biyo bayan karuwar masu cutar korona a Spain, inda aka samu karin mutane sama da 900 da suka kamu da cutar a ranar Juma'a.
Har ila yau, jami'an Spaniya sun yi gargadin cewa za a iya kusantar wani zango na biyu yayin da manyan biranen kasar suka ga alamun kamuwa da cutar.
Airlines da suka hada da British Airways sun soki sabbin matakan a matsayin "babu wani abu" ga masu biki na Birtaniya.
Mutane a halin yanzu a lokacin hutu a Spain an shawarci ma'aikatar Sufuri da su bi ka'idodin gida, su koma gida kamar yadda al'ada, da kuma duba ofishin harkokin waje ta travel shawara website don ƙarin bayani.
Ofishin harkokin waje yana ba da shawara game da duk tafiye-tafiye mai mahimmanci zuwa yankin Spain, duk da haka matakan killacewa sun shafi waɗanda suka dawo daga yankin Spain, da Kanary Islands da Balearic Islands, kamar Majorca da Ibiza.
Ofishin harkokin waje shawara yana da ramuwa ga tafiya inshora.
Daga cikin wadanda sabbin dokoki suka shafa akwai Sakataren sufuri Grant Shapps, wanda ya fara hutunsa a Spain a ranar Asabar.
Ana sa ran zai ci gaba da tafiyarsa kamar yadda aka tsara kuma ya ware bisa ga ja - gorar dawowarsa.
An fara gabatar da matakan kariya ga matafiya na Burtaniya a farkon watan Yuni.
Amma bayan matsin lamba daga masana'antun jirgin sama da tafiye-tafiye, gwamnati da kuma gwamnatocin da suka rage sun buga jerin kasashen da aka kebe daga ka'idojin.
Kamfanin British Airways ya ce an "sakamako" game da sabbin sauye-sauye ga shawarar tafiye-tafiye da dokoki na gwamnati, ko da yake kamfanin jirgin ya ce jiragensa na ci gaba da aiki.
Ya ce matakin ya "karfafa dubban tafiye-tafiyen da Britons ke yi cikin hargitsi."
Hukumar Kula da Jiragen Sama ta ce sabbin matakan za su "kashe abin da aka riga aka fara fara farawa a bangaren jirgin wanda ke ci gaba da fuskantar kalubale mafi girma a tarihinta."
Babban mai kula da yawon bude ido na Birtaniya, Tui, ya soke zirga-zirgar jiragen sama saboda ya tashi zuwa yankin Spain da tsibirin Kanary a ranar Lahadi.
Abokan ciniki a halin yanzu a lokacin hutu za su iya komawa a kan nufin jirgin gida.
Duk da haka, kamfanin jirgin sama na EasyJet ya ce an "sakamako" kuma zai gudanar da cikakken jadawalin a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
"Customers da suka daina so su yi tafiya za su iya canjawa su flights ba tare da wani canji fee ko kuma karɓar wani kudi don darajar booking," kamfanin ya ce a wata sanarwa.
Wani mai magana da yawun Hukumar Kula da Tafiya ta Birtaniya (Abta) ya ce canjin sarautar da gwamnati ta ke yi na "rashin fahimta."
"Muna bayar da shawarar cewa gwamnati ta yi la'akari da ɗaukar ka'idojin keɓewa don zirga-zirgar jiragen sama zuwa da kuma daga wasu yankuna da ke da ƙananan hanyoyin kamuwa da cutar, ko kuma zuwa wurare kamar Tsibirin Balearic ko kuma Kankana - waɗanda ke da bambanci a yankin Spain - don kauce wa ƙarin lalacewar masana'antu na yawon bude ido da ke cikin Birtaniya", in ji shi.
Spain ya zuwa yanzu ta ga mutuwar mutane fiye da 28,000.
A ranar Alhamis din da ta gabata, ta ga karuwar cututtuka mafi girma a kullum tun bayan da aka ƙare dokar kulle.
Catalonia ya zama sabon yankin da za a rushe a kan dare.
Yankin arewa maso gabas mai arziki, wanda ke gida Barcelona, ya ba da umarnin rufe dukkan wuraren shakatawa na dare har tsawon makonni biyu kuma ya sanya dokar hana fita ta tsakar dare a kan sanduna a yankin Barcelona mafi girma.
Wakilin BBC Guy Hedgecoe a Madrid ya ce rikice-rikice a tsakanin matasa wata damuwa ce, kamar yadda suka yi tattaki a manyan birane da dare.
Faransa ta gargadi 'yan kasarta da kada su yi tafiya zuwa Catalonia yayin da Norway ta ce za ta fara neman mutanen da suka isa Spain.
Gwamnatin tana kira ga ma'aikata da su kasance "fahimtar wadanda suka dawo daga Spain wadanda yanzu za su bukaci a ware kansu."
Amma sakataren gidauniyar shadow Labour Nick Thomas-Symonds ya bukaci gwamnati da ta yi bayani dalla-dalla kan yadda za ta tallafa wa wadanda abin ya shafa, inda ya kara da cewa labaran za su kasance "sabuwar damuwa ga iyalan da ke kamawa a Spain ko kuma suke shirin tafiya".
Ministan Farko na Scotland Nicola Sturgeon ya bayyana cewa an yanke shawarar ne bayan sake nazarin sabbin bayanai a ranar Asabar.
"Wannan ya ƙarfafa batun cewa waɗannan al'amura suna fuskantar canji a gajeren lokaci kuma don haka shawarara ita ce ta yi taka tsan-tsan game da tafiye-tafiyen kasashen waje da ba su da muhimmanci," in ji ta.
John Blackmore, daga Hampshire, an saboda ya tashi zuwa iyalinsa a Spain tare da matarsa da kananan yara biyu.
Amma sabon dokoki na nufin ya soke, domin fargabar matarsa m ba zai iya saukar da ita shan karin makonni biyu kashe don kebe a kan su dawo.
Ya ce ya yi tsammanin ba zai yiwu ba za su samu biyan kuɗin jirgin, kamar yadda ba a soke shi ba.
"Ina fatattaka", ya shaida wa BBC.
"Ina da iyali a Spain waɗanda ba su gan su kawai grandkids tun Kirsimeti."
Lois Stothard, daga South Yorkshire, ya gaya wa BBC cewa ta kama hutu zuwa Sevilla a matsayin abin mamaki ga saurayinta na 30th birthday - saboda tashi daga ranar Lahadi da safe - amma yanzu yana jin cewa ba za ta iya tafiya ba.
"Ni ma'aikaci ne - ni malami ne - kuma saurayina yana da alkawarin aiki don haka ba za mu iya keɓewa ba har tsawon kwanaki 14 idan muka dawo," in ji ta.
"Ba za mu iya samun wani kudi da baya da kuma canza kamfanin so biyu abin da na riga na biya a kudade.
Ina cike da takaici da damuwa yayin da muke cike da shirye-shiryen tafiya."
Ted Cruz ya ce manufofin Pelosi na "kashe tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka"
Washington - Sanata Ted Cruz na Republican na jihar Texas ya zargi kakakin majalisar wakilai Nancy Pelosi da 'yan majalisa da tura wani kunshin tallafin coronavirus da ke mayar da hankali kan "shoveling tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe Amurka" yayin da ake ci gaba da tattaunawa kan ma'auni na gaba.
A wata hira da ya yi da "Face the Nation" a ranar Lahadi, Cruz ya ce kasar na fuskantar bala'i biyu a lokaci guda: annobar duniya da ta yi sanadiyar rayukan mutane fiye da 600,000 a duk duniya da kuma "mummunar bala'in tattalin arziki" a Amurka.
Amma Cruz ya ce Pelosi, wadda ta bayyana a kan "Face the Nation" a gaban Sanatan, "ta damu ba daga cikin waɗanda."
"Manufofinta suna shoveling tsabar kudi a matsalar da kuma rufe America," in ji Texas Republican.
"Kuma musamman ma, ka dubi kudi dala tiriliyan da ta ke kokarin turawa, shi ne kawai shoveling kudi ga abokanta kuma ba a zahiri warware matsalar. Manufarmu ya kamata Amurkawa so su dawo aiki. Suna so su iya samar wa iyalinsu."
'Yan majalisar dattijai da fadar White House sun shafe makon da ya gabata suna tattaunawa kan sharuddan kashi na hudu na martanin coronavirus, wanda suke sa ran za su kashe dala tiriliyan 1.
A karshen mako, shugaban ma'aikatan fadar White House Mark Meadows da Sakataren Baitulmalin Amurka Steven Mnuchin sun koma Capitol Hill domin karin tattaunawa da ma'aikatan Majalisar Dattawa, kuma Mnuchin ya gaya wa Fox News a wata hira da suka yi a ranar Lahadi cewa za a bayyana cikakken bayani da Shugaban Majalisar Dattawa Mitch McConnell a ranar Litinin.
Batun da ya fi daukar hankali ga 'yan majalisar - da kuma wani batu da ke tsakanin 'yan Republicans da 'yan Democrats - shi ne zaburar da karin amfanin marasa aikin yi, wanda ya fara tafiya a wannan karshen mako.
Duk da yake 'yan Democrats suna son kunshin "lokaci hudu" na coronavirus don ci gaba da haɓaka $ 600 don amfanin, 'yan Republicans suna kira da a pared ta baya da kuma jayayya da wasu Amurkawa suna yin karin daga rashin aikin yi fiye da yadda suka yi a albashi.
Cruz ya ce fiye da rabin Amurkawa da ke samun amfanin rashin aikin yi da aka fi biyan su yanzu fiye da lokacin da suke aiki kuma ya ce ya yi magana da masu kananan kasuwanci a Texas wadanda suke samun matsala wajen farfado da ma'aikata.
"Tabbas, ba za su dawo ba saboda gwamnatin tarayya tana biyan su, a wasu lokuta, sau biyu a matsayin kudi mai yawa don su zauna a gida," in ji shi.
Cruz ya ce Congress ya kamata a mayar da hankali a kan wucewa da wani dawo da doka da zai sa ya fi sauki ga Amurkawa su koma aiki ta hanyar sassauta haraji da kuma ka'idoji a kan kananan kasuwanci: "Kamar kawai shoveling tiriliyans daga kofa, wani dawo da doka zai dakatar da biyan haraji, wanda zai ba shi a biya tada ga kowa a Amurka da ke aiki. Wannan a zahiri samun mutane koma ga aiki," ya ce.
Shugaba Trump ya bukaci a makon da ya gabata kunshin taimako na gaba sun hada da rage harajin albashi, amma Mnuchin ya ce ba zai zama wani ɓangare na dokokin ba, kamar yadda kudurin ya yi rashin lafiya a tsakanin Republicans.
Mr. Trump ya yarda da yanke harajin albashi zai kasance ba daga lissafin na gaba ba amma ya nemi ya dora laifi a kan Democrats.
Cruz, wanda a makon da ya gabata ya yi watsi da kudin kunshin na gaba, ya ce ranar Lahadi ba shi da ma'auni daga 'yan majalisar dattawan kasarsa.
Amma kuma ya soki kudurin dala tiriliyan 3 da majalisar Democrat-controlled House ta zartar a watan Mayu, kuma ya zargi abokan adawarsa na siyasa da gangan wajen tsara ma'aunin da ke lalata shugaban kasa gabanin zaben watan Nuwamba.
"Abin da kawai Democrats suke da shi shi ne su kayar da Donald Trump, kuma sun yi cynically yanke shawarar hanya mafi kyau don kayar da Donald Trump an rufe kowane kasuwanci a Amurka, rufe kowane makaranta a Amurka," in ji shi.
"Ka sani, Nancy Pelosi ta yi magana game da aiki maza da mata. Abin da ta ke bayarwa shi ne kiyaye aiki maza da mata daga aiki."
Rahul Gandhi Ya Goyi Bayan Mutanen Rajasthan
Rahul Gandhi na jam'iyyar Congress ya fadi wani bidiyo a yau yunƙurin wayar da kan jama'a a kan jam'iyyar BJP kan abubuwan da suka faru a Rajasthan.
Ta amfani da hashtag #SpeakUpForDemocracy, sakonsa na Hindia ya bukaci jama'a da su "Unite and raise our voice for democracy."
Jam’iyyar Congress tana shirin gudanar da zanga-zanga a kasar a ranar Litinin kan halin da ake ciki a Rajasthan, inda gwamnatin Ashok Gehlot ke faman tsira.
Yayin da jam'iyyar ta ce za a gudanar da zanga-zanga a wajen Rashtrapati Bhavan, fadar shugaban kasar Ram Nath Kovind.
A cikin bidiyon, jam'iyyar Congress ta zargi jam'iyyar BJP da "sakar da kundin tsarin mulki da rushe demokradiyya" yayin da dukan kasar ke fama da cutar korona.
Ya yi haka ne a Madhya Pradesh, in ji Congress.
"Muna bukatar a yi zaman taro nan take wanda ke cikin tsarin mulkinmu," in ji jam'iyyar a cikin bidiyon.
Gwamnan jihar Rajasthan Kalraj Mishra ya saukar da wani tsari na fara zaman taro.
An ƙaddamar da wani abu na biyu a yau wanda ya ce yana bincika.
Gwamnatin Mr Gehlot ta shiga cikin mawuyacin hali bayan da mataimakinsa Sachin Pilot ya yi tawaye tare da wasu manyan MLAs da ke goyon bayansa.
Jam'iyyar ba ta iya korar 'yan tawayen don su kawo alamar mafi rinjaye a cikin taron ba.
Mr Pilot -- wanda aka kwace daga cikin posts a cikin jam'iyyar da kuma gwamnati -- an ba da taimako na wucin gadi daga disqualification da Rajasthan High Court, wanda ya gudanar da cewa kakakin ba zai iya daukar wani mataki ba har sai da ya fi girma kundin tsarin mulki tambaya game da ikonsa aka yanke.
Kotun koli za ta yi wannan tambayar ne a gobe, wadda kuma za ta yanke hukunci kan ko wata kotu za ta iya tsoma bakin kakakin majalisar.
The Congress tsaye kawai daya baya da mafi rinjaye alama a cikin 200-majalisar.
Team Pilot ya yi ikirarin goyon bayan 30 MLAs, amma ya zuwa yanzu, hujjojin sun nuna zuwa 19.
Jam'iyyar BJP tana da mutane 72 da suka hada da kawayenta da masu zaman kansu, tana da 97.
Idan kotu ta yanke shawarar amincewa da Mr Pilot, Majalisa za ta iya rasa na biyu daga cikin gwamnatoci uku da ta kafa a jihohin kasar nan da suka biyo bayan zaben gama gari na 2018.
A watan Maris, ta rasa gwamnatin Kamal Nath-led a Madhya Pradesh bayan Jyotiraditya Scindia ya shiga jam'iyyar BJP tare da 22 daga cikin MLAs.
An kama jami'an 'yan sandan Kenya bayan harbe-harbe a Garissa
An kama wasu jami'an 'yan sanda biyu a Kenya dangane da harbin da aka yi a inda aka kashe mutane biyu.
Harin ya faru ne a kasuwar Soko Ng'ombe da ke gabashin karamar hukumar Garissa a ranar Asabar, yayin zanga-zangar nuna rashin amincewa da kama wani mutum da ake zargi da kisan kai.
An bayyana sunayen mutanen biyu a matsayin Aden Abdi Madobe da Muhiyadin Adow Shibin.
