Masu gangamin sun nuna damuwa game da aikin policing a lokacin annobar.
A cewar Amnesty International, jami'an Kenya sun kashe mutane 21 tun watan Maris saboda rashin bin matakan rigakafin coronavirus kamar dokar hana fita da rufe fuska.
