Shivraj Singh Chouhan Kan Gwajin Cutar Covid
Madhya Pradesh Chief Minister Shivraj Singh Chouhan, wanda a ranar Asabar ya tabbatar da cewa ya kamu da cutar COVID-19, ya fada a ranar Lahadi da safe ya ce ya "kashe" kuma ya bayar da yabo ga ma'aikatan gaba-gaba a yaki da cutar korona.
Babban Ministan ya kuma sake maimaita gargadinsa daga jiya, lokacin da ya bukaci mutane da su bi ka'idodi, kamar zaman jama'a da kuma amfani da takunkumin fuska.
"Ina lafiya, abokaina. Keɓe kan mayaƙan coronavirus, waɗanda ke haɗa rayuwarsu da kansu, abin yabo ne. Ina jinjina wa dukkan mayaƙan coronavirus na jihar", in ji Mr Chouhan daga asibitin Bhopal na Chirayu, inda aka shigar da shi jiya.
"Ka yi nisan mita biyu, ka wanke hannayenka akai-akai kuma ka sanya takunkumin fuska - wadannan su ne manyan makamai da muke da su don kauce wa cutar coronavirus. Ina roƙo ga dukan mutane - ka yi amfani da waɗannan makamai don kanka da kuma ƙaunatattunka," in ji shi.
"Duk kana da hankali, ka zauna lafiya da lafiya. Wannan shi ne abin da nake addu'a ga Allah," Mr Chouhan ya kara da cewa.
A ranar Asabar ne Mista Chouhan ya bayyana cewa ya yi gwajin cutar duk da kokarin da yake yi na kauce wa kamuwa da cutar kuma ya yi gargadin cewa "rashin kulawa kawai yana kiran cutar coronavirus".
Tweeting this morning Mr Chouhan ya ce duk da barazanar kamuwa da cutar akwai "babu bukatar tsoro" kuma ya bukaci wadanda ke nuna alamun cutar su gwada kansu.
"Idan kun kamu da cutar, babu buƙatar tsoro. Kada ku ɓoye alamun cutar amma ku gaya wa likitoci nan da nan, don haka za a iya fara magani.
Madhya Pradesh na da kusan mutum 27,000 da suka kamu da COVID-19, wanda fiye da 7,600 suke aiki kuma 799 ne suka mutu da cutar.
Indiya ta samu karuwar wadanda suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a makonnin da suka gabata, inda aka gano sabbin kamuwa 45,000 a kowace rana tun ranar 23 ga watan Yuli.
Adadin wadanda aka tabbatar sun kamu da cutar coronavirus yana da saurin zuwa 14 lakh; daga cikin wadannan fiye da 4.67 lakh masu aiki ne kuma fiye da 32,000 ne suka mutu sanadiyyar cutar.
A ci gaba da kamuwa da cutar, coinciding with the staggered relaxation of lockdown guidelines a non-containment zones na kasar, ya yada India zuwa uku a jerin al'ummomin da abin ya shafa.
Sai dai Amurka (41.78 lakh cases) da Brazil (23.94 lakh cases) sun fi muni.
Ministan cikin gida na Tunisia ya nada sabon PM, don kafa gwamnati cikin wata guda
An nada ministan cikin gida na kasar Tunisia Hichem Mechichichi, ya kafa gwamnati ta gaba, inji ofishin shugaban kasar, a yayin da ake fama da tashe-tashen hankula tsakanin manyan jam'iyyun kasar ta Arewacin Afirka.
Lauya mai shekaru 46 ya yi nasara a kan Elyes Fakhfakh, wanda ya yi murabus a matsayin firayim minista a farkon wannan watan.
Amma Mechichi ba daya daga cikin sunayen da hukumar jam'iyyun siyasa suka gabatar ga shugaban kasar Kais Saied.
A cikin wata sanarwa da ta fitar a ranar Asabar, Mechichi ya ce zai "yi aiki don kafa gwamnatin da ta sadu da tsammanin dukkan 'yan Tunisiya."
Tunisiya an yaba a matsayin wani labari mai ban sha'awa na samun nasara don sauyin demokradiyya bayan tashe-tashen hankula na yankin Larabawa da aka yi a shekarar 2011.
Amma shugabanninta sun yi ta kokawa wajen biyan bukatun al'ummar Tunisiya kuma tattalin arzikin da ya riga ya ci tura ta hanyar rufe iyakokin kasar saboda annobar COVID-19.
Cutar ta kashe kusan mutane 50 kuma ta kama fiye da 1,400 a Tunisia.
Kazalika kasancewa ministan cikin gida a gwamnatin waje, Mechichi ya kasance mai ba da shawara ga shugaban kasar Saied, wajen tafiyar da al'amuran shari'a.
A baya ya kasance shugaban ma'aikata a ma'aikatar sufuri kuma ya yi aiki a ma'aikatar zamantakewar jama'a.
Yanzu yana da wata guda da zai kafa gwamnati, wanda daga nan zai fuskanci kuri'ar amincewa na majalisar dokoki kuma zai bukaci cikakken rinjaye don samun nasara.
Kasancewar hakan, za a narke majalisar kuma za a gudanar da sabon zabe cikin watanni uku.
A zaben da ya gabata da aka gudanar a watan Oktoba, jam'iyyar Ennahdha ta zo a kan gaba amma ta yi kasa da rinjaye kuma daga bisani ta amince ta shiga gwamnatin hadaka.
Fakhfakh ya yi murabus a ranar 15 ga watan Yuli, bayan kasa da watanni biyar a kan mukaminsa, ya yi barazanar sake fasalin siyasa a cikin al'umma yayin da yake fama da matsalar tattalin arziki da ake fama da ita.
Yin murabus din ya zurfafa rikicin siyasa da Ennahdha kan zargin da ake yi wa Fakhfakh na rikice-rikice masu sha’awa.
Dangantaka tsakanin shugaba mai shekaru 47 da Ennahdha ta taso tun bayan zaben majalisar dokoki na watan Oktoba.
Fakhfakh ya sauka a rana guda bayan da jam’iyyar ta shigar da kara ba bisa ka’ida ba.
Ennahdha da farko ya zabi wani mai zaman kanta ga firayim minista, amma ya kasa samun goyon bayan majalisar dokoki, ya jagoranci shugaban kasar ya sunan tsohon ministan kudi Fakhfakh domin post.
Faced with the prospect of fresh elections, Ennahdha daga bisani ya amince ya shiga gwamnatin hadaka.
Mo na tururuwa ta wurin taron jama'a, mai zanga-zanga ya harbe shi a Colorado
AURORA, Colo. (AP) - Wata mota ta afkawa jama'a kuma an harbe wani mai zanga-zanga a unguwar Denver da ke Aurora a lokacin da ake zanga-zanga kan rashin adalcin launin fata.
Rundunar 'yan sandan Aurora ta bayyana a shafinta na Twitter cewa masu zanga-zangar suna tafiya ne a kan Interstate 225 ranar Asabar lokacin da wata motar ta bi ta.
'Yan sanda sun ce wani mai zanga-zanga ya harba wani makami, yana daukan akalla mutum guda da aka kai asibiti cikin kwanciyar hankali.
Mahukunta sun ce motar da aka kona kuma suna bincike.
Masu zanga-zanga sun kuma fasa tagogi zuwa gidan yari kuma an fara bude wuta a wani ofishin, in ji 'yan sanda.
An ayyana haramtaccen taro kuma 'yan sanda sun umarci masu zanga-zanga su bar yankin, in ji hukumomi.
An yi tashin hankali a zanga-zangar da aka yi a baya-bayan nan kan rashin adalcin launin fata tun lokacin da aka tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya don yin zanga-zanga a Portland, Oregon.
'Yan sanda sun bayyana tarzoma a Seattle a ranar Asabar.
Zanga-zangar da aka yi ta janyo mutuwar George Floyd a ranar 25 ga watan Mayu, wani bakar fata a Minnesota da ya mutu bayan da wani farar fata ya rike shi a ƙasa tare da gwiwa zuwa wuyansa, sun kuma nanata wasu lokuta na mummunan tashin hankalin 'yan sanda.
A jihar Colorado, masu zanga-zangar sun maida hankali ne kan mutuwar Elijah McClain, wanda 'yan sanda suka tsaya yayin da suke tafiya a kan titin Aurora a watan Agustan 2019 bayan da wani mai kira 911 ya ba da rahotonsa a matsayin mai ba da hankali.
’Yan sanda sun sanya shi a cikin chokehold, kuma likitoci sun sarrafa milligrams 500 na ketamine, najasa, don kwantar da shi.
Ya shiga cikin binciken kwakwaf, daga baya aka bayyana kwakwalwa ta mutu kuma aka kashe tallafin rayuwa.
Fam bayyana Lake Tahoe da aka gurɓata da sauyin yanayi
South Lake Tahoe, California - Duk da annobar, ko a ranar mako, mutane har yanzu suna taron Pope Beach a Lake Tahoe.
