Cutar Salmonella ta ci mutum 212 a jihohi 23
25 ga Yuli (UPI) -- Cibiyar kula da cututtuka da rigakafi tana binciken barkewar cutar salmonella da ta yi wa mutane 212 ciwo a jihohi 23.
A cikin wata sanarwar manema labarai ta ranar Juma'a, CDC ta bayyana cewa mutane 87 sun kamu da rashin lafiya tun bayan sabuntawarta na karshe a ranar Talata.
Hukumar ta ce mutane sun fara nuna alamun da ke da nasaba da nau'in salmonella, wanda zai iya daukar makonni biyu zuwa hudu don bayyana alamun, tsakanin 19 ga Yuni zuwa 11 ga Yuli.
An kwantar da mutane talatin da daya a asibiti tun bayan da aka fara samun barkewar cutar, amma ba a samu rahoton wadanda suka mutu ba.
A cewar CDC, ba a gano ainihin tushen cutar salmonella ba.
Ba ta bayar da wani shawara game da cin abinci ko cinye musamman abinci ba, ko kuma masu sayar da suna da za a iya sayar da kayayyakin gurbatattu.
Oregon na da mafi yawan lokuta na salmonella, tare da 51 masu kamuwa da cutar, tare da Utah bayan kusa da 40 da aka ruwaito.
Salmonella cuta ce ta bakteriya, rashin lafiyar abinci da ke haifar da cututtuka miliyan 1.35, asibiti 26,500, da kuma mutuwar 420 a kowace shekara, a cewar CDC.
Mafi yawan alamun kamuwa da cutar salmonella sune cutar zawo, zazzabi, da ciwon ciki, wanda zai iya farawa tsakanin sa'o'i shida da kwanaki shida bayan kamuwa da cutar.
Rashin lafiya yana yawan tsawon kwanaki hudu zuwa bakwai, kuma yawancin mutane suna warkewa ba tare da magani ba, amma wasu lokuta suna buƙatar asibiti.
